Some Water Safety Tips:

Always stay within arm’s reach of young children and avoid distractions, such as cell phones.
Reach or throw aid to distressed swimmers, don’t go in!
Keep toys not in use away from the pool and out of sight.
Drowning is silent and nobody is drown proof.
